            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Hd1e108">Rubrica 8</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De rixis et scandalis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>
      ¶ De rixis et scandalis. Rubrica. 8.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="27"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e115">SAlomon in prouerb. c. 10</ref>
      <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e125">Odium suscitat
        <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>rixas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e131"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e127">15. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e133">Uir iracundus prouocat
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>rixas: qui patiens est mitigatur susci
        <lb ed="#V" n="31" break="no"/>tatas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e142"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e140">18. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e144">Labia stulti immiscent se rixis:
        <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>et os eius iurgia prouocat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e150">
               <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e152">Iesus filius sirach in eccl. c. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e154">Cum iracundo
        <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>non facies rixam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e160"> /
            <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e162">27.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e162">Effusio sanguinis in
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>rixam superborum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e168">
               <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e174">Mattheus in euangel. c. 18.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e172">Uhe mundo a
        <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>scandalis. Necesse est vt veniant scandala:
        <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>veruntamen vhe homini per quem scandalum venit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e180">
               <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e188">Cato. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e184">Rumores fuge: ne incipias no
        <lb ed="#V" n="40" break="no"/>uus auctor haberi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e190">
               <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e200">Isidorus solilo. li. 2. et fi. c. 26</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e194">Fuge rixam</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e199">
               <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e211">Iacobus beneuentanus. c. 5.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="43"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e203">Lingua odium parit: et faciet tibi litem.
        <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>Effreni lingua: surgere bella solent.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-d1e211">
               <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Rd1e224">Prouerb. vulgar.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34168-Qd1e215">Del can grintoso: eno<!--116.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="46" break="no"/>forroso guai la pelle.</quote>
            </p>
